        <description lang="da_DK">Neo Geo Pocket var en håndholdt konsol med en monokrom skærm udgivet af SNK i 1998. Den var generelt ikke en succes og blev i 1999 erstattet af Neo Geo Pocket Color for bedre at kunne konkurrere med Game Boy Color.</description>
        <description lang="en_GB">The Neo Geo Pocket was a handheld console with a monochrome screen released by SNK in 1998. It was generally unsuccessful and in 1999 was replaced by the Neo Geo Pocket Color to better compete with the Game Boy Color.</description>
        <description lang="zh_CN">Neo Geo Pocket 是 SNK 于1998年发布的一款带有单色屏幕的便携式游戏机。为更好地与 Game Boy Color 竞争，这款不成功产品于1999年被 Neo Geo Pocket Color 取代。</description>
